{"tid":1411011,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今次係一場出於良知嘅革命","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:13:59.000Z","uid":173326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d4b231298e1a920ed6f8320355dbf5b9b5f3d4","tid":1411011,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6月，有好多人出來表達政治訴求、反對暴政。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">7月，仍然有6月個批人，但亦多左更多人係為左反對警黑勾結、反對黑警濫權。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>8月，6月、7月嘅人仍然出嚟，但亦多左好多街坊鄰居。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到今日，無論係出嚟遊行集會嘅，定係網上口誅筆伐嘅，全部都係出於良知而發聲！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為左生活我可以忍、可以冇民主自由，但埋沒良知、縱容黑警暴政殘害平民就唔可以！</span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1264f5cb9229eec676221585ea1f8b2ee1a47714","tid":1411011,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"多多錢都買唔到良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b642aa448d4fa99abb054cd73bcd01978b9e3ae8","tid":1411011,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"根本就係良知革命，<br />\n當你為左一日生計可以唔要良知，<br />\n咁香港真係唔係咁岩你。"},{"pid":"1b62d72ff6fd54ce0feb9623b0ecec9b3e70fc78","tid":1411011,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b642aa448d4fa99abb054cd73bcd01978b9e3ae8","tid":1411011,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"根本就係良知革命，<br />\n當你為左一日生計可以唔要良知，<br />\n咁香港真係唔係咁岩你。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"冇左份工都要發聲，如果唔係就同64事件時嘅民眾一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c085545917cfcdf0346997fc6d3ead0c5403e5e"